            <title>苹果 watchOS 26.5 开发者预览版 Beta 4 发布</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/944/202.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/944/202.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 17:47:24 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p style="text-align: center;">【<a href="https://www.ithome.com/0/944/202.htm#profile-download">点此直达升级教程</a>】</p><p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 4 月 28 日消息，苹果今日向 Apple Watch 用户推送了 watchOS 26.5 开发者预览版 Beta 4 更新（内部版本号：23T5568a），本次更新距离上次发布 Beta / RC 间隔 7 天。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="苹果 watchOS26 操作系统" height="600" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2025/12/1a5f474f-41a2-4962-a5a9-6b3780e56fde.jpg?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEzOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_7,y_14,x_14,a_0/format,f_auto" title="苹果 watchOS 26.5 开发者预览版 Beta 4 发布" width="800" /> </p><h2 class="ai-word-checked" id="profile-download">如何升级 iOS / iPadOS / watchOS / macOS 开发版和公测版？</h2><p>• <strong>公开测试版</strong>：需注册&nbsp;<a href="https://beta.apple.com/zh-CN/guide#ios" target="_blank" title="Apple Beta 版软件计划">Apple Beta 版软件计划</a>，之后通过【设置】【通用】【软件更新】【Beta 版更新】来升级；</p><p>• <strong>开发预览版</strong>：需登录注册<a href="https://developer.apple.com/programs/" target="_blank" title="苹果开发者计划">苹果开发者计划</a>，之后通过【设置】【通用】【软件更新】来升级。</p><h3 class="ai-word-checked">附苹果 iOS 历史固件下载大全：</h3><p class="ai-word-checked">《<a href="https://www.ithome.com/iosfirmware" target="_blank" title="苹果 iOS / iPadOS / macOS 固件下载 / 更新日志大全">苹果 iOS / iPadOS / macOS 固件下载 / 更新日志大全</a>》</p><p>目前尚无关于软件具体内容的任何消息。watchOS、tvOS 和 visionOS 的每个新测试版通常新增功能不多，更新主要集中在 Bug 修复和性能提升上。前三个测试版均未发现任何新功能。</p><h3>附 watchOS 26 发布历史：</h3><ul class="custom_reference list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/941/379.htm" target="_blank">2026-04-21：watchOS 26.5 Beta 3 (23T5558e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/938/749.htm" target="_blank">2026-04-14：watchOS 26.5 Beta 2 (23T5553d)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/934/275.htm" target="_blank">2026-03-31：watchOS 26.5 Beta (23T5541h)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/932/305.htm" target="_blank">2026-03-25：watchOS 26.4 (23T240)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/930/444.htm" target="_blank">2026-03-19：watchOS 26.4 RC (23T239)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/927/390.htm" target="_blank">2026-03-10：watchOS 26.4 Beta 4 (23T5236a)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/925/214.htm" target="_blank">2026-03-03：watchOS 26.4 Beta 3 (23T5226e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/923/010.htm" target="_blank">2026-02-24：watchOS 26.4 Beta 2 (23T5221e)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/922/156.htm" target="_blank">2026-02-17：watchOS 26.4 Beta (23T5209m)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/921/235.htm" target="_blank">2026-02-12：watchOS 26.3 (23S620)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/919/310.htm" target="_blank">2026-02-05：watchOS 26.3 RC (23S618)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/916/642.htm" target="_blank">2026-01-27：watchOS 26.2.1 (23S314)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p><a class="breakall" href="https://www.ithome.com/0/916/650.htm" target="_blank">2026-01-27：watchOS 26.3 Beta 3 (23S5611c)</a></p></li><li class="list-undefined list-reference-paddingleft"><p