净，只有果仁无其他。</p><p>高品质包材，经得起开封回潮考验，长效香脆锁鲜，每次开罐都像是刚出厂。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1113" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/f11fd8ed-06e0-4afb-b150-703821d29f28.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="嘴这辈子跟了我也是值了：天虹混合坚果 2 斤百补 101 元，开心果碧根果腰果仁" width="835" />、<img height="896" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2026/4/4908d1b0-deec-4a2c-83eb-e66b2e0cfc67.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="嘴这辈子跟了我也是值了：天虹混合坚果 2 斤百补 101 元，开心果碧根果腰果仁" width="835" /></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p>需点击宝贝详情页<span class="font-color-red">“百亿补贴优惠券”红色横幅</span>下单哦：</p></li></ul><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://uland.taobao.com/coupon/edetail?e=w9ZiTmlSQdmlhHvvyUNXZfh8CuWt5YH5OVuOuRD5gLJMmdsrkidbOWBzzpT26idJUGInONGM6wyxCjvyoN4yWVn8PopUEwm8LSOpvkSz8xebuFE4qLrEY9%2BfSzCuQUP82mwCY5fS7rVrTdT7cgXf6jgYSYpxmYtMsb%2Bvi71p7YhlXymvoVZzQ0qo8R84sD7ymVISgPb07V6Ywek19h0d0NQV3tBpdKHodxJgRmH6PTUPrRT%2FGlevSUzgKIk6XTsliqP6wveQFBWrBNRUyvxLOEkn5iMJB93h9DHS%2B25on6jo1CSKBr4tRVInYAivpi9ODDhbHJaxYqF%2BOHfs5nLQGA%3D%3D&amp;traceId=2150465517772992916437453e0d29&amp;&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1777299291@0b830dfc_16dd_19dcf4afe50_e77e@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="640" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/O1CN01dezsRX1eJLyts5M4M_!!6000000003850-0-yinhe.jpg_640x640.jpg" title="嘴这辈子跟了我也是值了：天虹混合坚果 2 斤百补 101 元，开心果碧根果腰果仁" width="640" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">天虹牌 罐装混合坚果</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> 1kg</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 百亿补贴 100.9 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p><div class="tagging1">【广告】</div>
